AP VIII Queso Holdings, L.P. Overview
  AP VIII Queso Holdings, L.P. filed as a Foreign Limited Partnership in the State of New York on Friday, January 17, 2014 and is approximately three years old, according to public records filed with New York Department of State. A corporate filing is called a foreign filing when an existing corporate entity files in a state other than the state they originally filed in. This does not necessarily mean that they are from outside the United States. 




